[
  "div",
  {
    "className": "content-wrapper"
  },
  [
    "header",
    {
      "className": "lesson-header"
    },
    [
      "p",
      {
        "className": "lesson-meta"
      },
      "Lesson 29"
    ],
    [
      "h1",
      {},
      "Groups of Verbs"
    ]
  ],
  [
    "article",
    {},
    [
      "section",
      {},
      [
        "p",
        {},
        "In Greek, verbs are categorized into \"Conjugations\" (Συζυγίες) based\n            on their ending in the Present Tense. Knowing which group a verb\n            belongs to is essential for conjugating it correctly."
      ],
      [
        "div",
        {
          "className": "group-grid mt-8"
        },
        [
          "div",
          {
            "className": "group-card  first"
          },
          [
            "header",
            {},
            [
              "h3",
              {},
              "First Conjugation"
            ],
            [
              "span",
              {
                "className": "ending"
              },
              "-ω (unaccented)"
            ]
          ],
          [
            "div",
            {
              "className": "content"
            },
            [
              "p",
              {},
              "Verbs ending in",
              " ",
              [
                "strong",
                {},
                "-ω"
              ],
              " ",
              "where the accent is on\n                        the stem."
            ],
            [
              "ul",
              {
                "className": "example-list"
              },
              [
                "li",
                {},
                [
                  "span",
                  {
                    "className": "greek-text"
                  },
                  "τρέχω"
                ],
                " ",
                "(I run)"
              ],
              [
                "li",
                {},
                [
                  "span",
                  {
                    "className": "greek-text"
                  },
                  "παίζω"
                ],
                " ",
                "(I play)"
              ]
            ]
          ]
        ],
        [
          "div",
          {
            "className": "group-card  second"
          },
          [
            "header",
            {},
            [
              "h3",
              {},
              "Second Conjugation"
            ],
            [
              "span",
              {
                "className": "ending"
              },
              "-ώ (accented)"
            ]
          ],
          [
            "div",
            {
              "className": "content"
            },
            [
              "p",
              {},
              "Verbs ending in",
              " ",
              [
                "strong",
                {},
                "-ώ"
              ],
              " ",
              "where the accent is on\n                        the last syllable."
            ],
            [
              "ul",
              {
                "className": "example-list"
              },
              [
                "li",
                {},
                [
                  "span",
                  {
                    "className": "greek-text"
                  },
                  "αγαπώ"
                ],
                " ",
                "(I love)"
              ],
              [
                "li",
                {},
                [
                  "span",
                  {
                    "className": "greek-text"
                  },
                  "νικώ"
                ],
                " ",
                "(I win)"
              ]
            ]
          ]
        ],
        [
          "div",
          {
            "className": "group-card  passive"
          },
          [
            "header",
            {},
            [
              "h3",
              {},
              "Middle/Passive"
            ],
            [
              "span",
              {
                "className": "ending"
              },
              "-όμαι / -άμαι"
            ]
          ],
          [
            "div",
            {
              "className": "content"
            },
            [
              "p",
              {},
              "Verbs ending in",
              " ",
              [
                "strong",
                {},
                "-μαι"
              ],
              ". These often have\n                        a reflexive or passive meaning."
            ],
            [
              "ul",
              {
                "className": "example-list"
              },
              [
                "li",
                {},
                [
                  "span",
                  {
                    "className": "greek-text"
                  },
                  "κάθομαι"
                ],
                " ",
                "(I sit)"
              ],
              [
                "li",
                {},
                [
                  "span",
                  {
                    "className": "greek-text"
                  },
                  "κοιμάμαι"
                ],
                " ",
                "(I sleep)"
              ]
            ]
          ]
        ]
      ],
      [
        "div",
        {
          "className": "info-box  mt-12"
        },
        [
          "h3",
          {},
          "Why the Accent Matters"
        ],
        [
          "p",
          {},
          "The accent mark on the final",
          " ",
          [
            "strong",
            {},
            "-ώ"
          ],
          " ",
          "tells you that the\n                verb follows a different set of endings (often adding an extra -α-\n                in the conjugation)."
        ],
        [
          "p",
          {
            "className": "mt-4"
          },
          "Example: 1st Group",
          " ",
          [
            "strong",
            {},
            "τρέχ-εις"
          ],
          " ",
          "vs 2nd Group",
          " ",
          [
            "strong",
            {},
            "αγαπ-άς"
          ],
          "."
        ]
      ]
    ]
  ],
